OL,3,C'Holding a mirror to society': Stephen
OL,4,CGraham on his new series
OL,6,FActor Stephen Graham speaks to ITV
OL,7,FNews Arts Editor Nina Nannar about his
OL,8,Fnew series Adolescence
OL,10,FWhen I mentioned to friends and
OL,11,Fcolleagues that I was going to
OL,12,Finterview Stephen Graham, the
OL,13,Fresponses varied from 'he's my
OL,14,Ffavourite actor' to 'he's the greatest
OL,15,Factor in the world'.
OL,17,FWell, everyone's favourite actor is
OL,18,Fnot resting on his laurels.
