OL,3,C'Holding a mirror to society': Stephen
OL,4,CGraham on his new series
OL,6,FHis current project, Adolescence,
OL,7,Fwhich is on Netflix now, is some of
OL,8,Fthe most staggering television I've
OL,9,Fever seen.
OL,11,FFour hour-long episodes, dealing with
OL,12,Fa teenage boy accused of stabbing a
OL,13,Fschoolgirl to death, they delve into
OL,14,Fthemes of toxic masculinity, incels,
OL,15,Fthe malevolent impact the internet can
OL,16,Fhave on young minds, parental
OL,17,Finfluences - themes that will speak to
OL,18,Fmany, many families today.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
