OL,3,C'Holding a mirror to society': Stephen
OL,4,CGraham on his new series
OL,6,FIt's going to be a chilling watch for
OL,7,Fparents of teenagers, I say to Stephen
OL,8,FGraham, who created and wrote the
OL,9,Fseries with award-winning screenwriter
OL,10,FJack Thorne, and who also plays the
OL,11,Ffather of the accused 13-year-old boy.
OL,13,F"That's what it should be," he
OL,14,Freplies. "We were brought up on strong
OL,15,Ftelevision that was saying something,
OL,16,Flike Boys from the Blackstuff.
OL,18,F"We don't have the answers and we're
OL,19,Fnot saying that we do....but as a
OL,20,Fsociety we need to look at these kinds
OL,21,Fof things.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
