OL,3,C'Holding a mirror to society': Stephen
OL,4,CGraham on his new series
OL,6,F"We wanted to put a mirror up to
OL,7,Fsociety and just say take a little
OL,8,Flook and see what's going on."
OL,10,FHe points towards what he calls a
OL,11,Fpandemic of knife crime and says he
OL,12,Fand director Philip Barantini, came up
OL,13,Fwith the idea for the drama after
OL,14,Fhearing news stories of teenage
OL,15,Fstabbings, particularly of young boys
OL,16,Fattacking girls.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
