OL,3,C'Holding a mirror to society': Stephen
OL,4,CGraham on his new series
OL,6,FGraham admits then when he sees the
OL,7,Fnews, he can be quick to judge, like
OL,8,Fmany, and blame the parents. He wanted
OL,9,Fto highlight how that is not always
OL,10,Fthe case.
OL,12,F"There was no social media in our
OL,13,Fday," adds Barantini. "But there's so
OL,14,Fmuch out there now and it's so
OL,15,Faccessible.
OL,17,F"There are things that send kids down
OL,18,Fa rabbit hole and they believe that to
OL,19,Fbe true. It's a scary time. I've got
OL,20,Fan eight-year-old daughter and I'm
OL,21,Fscared for the future."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
