OL,3,C'Holding a mirror to society': Stephen
OL,4,CGraham on his new series
OL,6,FHe and Barantini have known each other
OL,7,Ffor 25 years, meeting as actors on the
OL,8,Fset of the US drama series Band of
OL,9,FBrothers, but their partnership soared
OL,10,Fto new heights when they made Boiling
OL,11,FPoint, the UK's first feature length
OL,12,Ffilm shot in one take.
OL,14,FSet in a frantic restaurant kitchen,
OL,15,Fit drew huge acclaim.
OL,17,FWith Adolescence they have taken
OL,18,Fthings to another level by making all
OL,19,Ffour episodes this way.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
