OL,3,C'Holding a mirror to society': Stephen
OL,4,CGraham on his new series
OL,6,FTwo cameras were used with the
OL,7,Foperators switching seamlessly from
OL,8,Fone to another so the shot could
OL,9,Fcontinue.
OL,11,FThere are thrilling scenes of police
OL,12,Fraids, and chases across streets and
OL,13,Fneighbourhoods.
OL,15,FTwo takes were shot a day over the
OL,16,Ffilming period, with the best one
OL,17,Feventually chosen for broadcast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
