OL,3,C'Holding a mirror to society': Stephen
OL,4,CGraham on his new series
OL,6,FBarantini, who directed the series,
OL,7,Fsaid the method allows for an
OL,8,Fimmersive experience with the viewers
OL,9,Falmost part of the action, sharing
OL,10,Fmoments of tension.
OL,12,FAmongst a stellar cast, including
OL,13,FGraham and Erin Doherty, is 14-year-
OL,14,Fold Owen Cooper, who plays the 13-year-
OL,15,Fold lead in the series, Jamie Cooper.
OL,17,FChosen from hundreds of other
OL,18,Fhopefuls, Cooper, who has never acted
OL,19,Fbefore, is a phenomenon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
