OL,3,C'Holding a mirror to society': Stephen
OL,4,CGraham on his new series
OL,6,FGraham has long made it an aim of his
OL,7,Fcompany Matriarch Productions, which
OL,8,Fhe co founded with his wife actress
OL,9,FHannah Walters, to champion
OL,10,Funderrepresented groups in TV and film.
OL,12,FSo to play the lead, he wanted a boy
OL,13,Fwho had not gone to theatre school.
OL,15,FOwen's family, Graham says, live in a
OL,16,Fcouncil house, and he is proud that
OL,17,Fthe drama team have given an
OL,18,Fopportunity to a talent that might
OL,19,Fotherwise have struggled to get a foot
OL,20,Fin the industry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
